msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Excuse me!\r\nCan I ask you a question, sir?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Hm? What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "This is pretty random,\r\nbut... uh... are you a yakuza?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I just, uh... I thought\r\nyou were a yakuza... Maybe...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "What do you have there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Oh, this thing?\r\nIt's a selfie stick!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Selfie... stick?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Moving on!\r\nYou're totally a yakuza, right? <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Right</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "I'm just a regular civilian.\r\nWhy would you even ask that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Huh!? Are you for real?\r\nYou don't look <font_kind=yakuza_italic>regular</font_kind> at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "It's a shame too,\r\ncause I've got some big plans, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "What are you talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Oh, how rude of me.\r\nMy name's Hiroshi Tsutsui."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "I'm rolling footage for a vid I'm calling\r\n\"Kamurocho Yakuza: Up Close and Personal.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Well? Pretty dank, huh?\r\nMy views are gonna be through the roof!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure I understand, but in this town,\r\nit's safer not to try anything stupid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Huh? Safety's nothing if it means realizing\r\nmy dream of going viral on the net!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Well, no time for chit-chat, man!\r\nI gotta go find a real yakuza, stat! Lates!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Are kids really that annoying now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Whaaat's up, guys!? Time for another vid\r\nfrom your boy, the Tsutsui-kun Channel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "So sad for us, we couldn't pin down a real\r\nyakuza last time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "But like they say, every second counts!\r\nSo here we are at<symbol=em_dash_with_outline> KaBLAM! The batting cages!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "We're going in for a fresh start down here at\r\nthe Yoshida Batting Center... without permission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Today, we're gonna test the <font_kind=yakuza_italic>so-called</font_kind> speed\r\nof their fastest fastball. Just how fast is it!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "...What is this guy's problem?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "All right, all right!\r\nC'mon, c'mon, c'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Ergh! Aghhh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Yep, he's serious..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "That one was off the hook, huh?\r\nThis time, we're getting even closer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Yow! Aghhh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "...Is he serious?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Excuse me, sir! Why are you doing that?\r\nStop it, right now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Q-Quiet, you! I paid the entry fee, so I can\r\ntake a ball to the balls if I want!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "You're out of your mind!\r\nI'm calling the cops!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Don't be an asshole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Hey, that's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Huh? You're that totally-a-yakuza\r\ncivilian from before!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Shooting another video? Take this\r\nridiculous hobby of yours elsewhere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Pffft. Whatever, I already got the bit.\r\nI'll be outta here in a sec."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "This is gonna be my breakout vid...!\r\nThe birth of the viral sensation, Tsutsui!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Hey, we weren't done here!\r\nMan, that guy's got a screw loose...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Him again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Dammit, what the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, it's you again...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Don't tell me<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>you're getting yourself\r\ninto trouble over here, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Well, that's rude!\r\nI'm just getting the creative juices flowing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Still... This blows. My crazy \"Fastball Fiasco\"\r\nvideo barely broke a couple hundred views!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Maybe you see yourself as some kind of star,\r\nbut all you're doing is causing trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "I understand how you feel, but if you want to\r\nget famous, you need to do it the right way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Keep your lectures to yourself.\r\nMy next vid... That'll be the one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Oh come on..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "S-Someone help me!\r\nAnyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "What the...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Somebody!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Anybody!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Him again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Help meee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "...What the hell was he thinking?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "You dumbass!\r\nTryin' such an obvious stunt on us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "I-I'm so sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Hey, you!\r\nSave me! Please!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Looks like you're finally getting the video you want.\r\nLet me guess<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>this will get you tons of views?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Never mind that! I'm over all that stuff!\r\nJust please get me down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Only if you erase all your videos and promise you'll\r\nnever come back to this city. How does that sound?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "It's a deal! I promise!\r\nJust help me already!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "All right, then.\r\nHang tight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "What? You look perfectly fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry, man.\r\nI didn't mean to draw attention."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "I was just teachin' this punk a lesson."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Right...\r\nWell, it's my bad for barging in here, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "I got it! Dangling upside-down at\r\nthe mercy of the yakuza... Sweet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Such raw intensity! This is my breakthrough!\r\nThis is trending material!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Hey, don't forget our deal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Huh? Pretty sure that was only if you saved me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "(This guy...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Hey, kid. I don't wanna tell you what to do,\r\nbut you should probably delete that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "No way! Uploading this baby'll get me 10k views!\r\nOr maybe... even the legendary million!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Hell yeah! Watch out world,\r\nhere comes the Tsutsui-kun Channel!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Your friend here has a point.\r\nDelete the video, kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "I told you I can't do that!\r\nWhat, you guys jealous or something!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "This is incredible, though.\r\nAfter \"Tsutsui-kun's Yakuza Mishap\" goes viral..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "...I'll put out \"Double Yakuza Takedown\"!\r\nIt'll be the perfect follow-up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "I've had it up to here with you.\r\nTime to teach you a lesson you won't forget!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "So? How'd your video turn out?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Either way, you're shit outta luck. You're gonna\r\nhave to delete that data right now. Cool?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Dammit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "I've got a good idea for a replacement, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Huh? You do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Here's the title."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "\"An Annoying Punk Apologizes For Everything.\"\r\nNow, shall we get filming?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Oh, that's a good one.\r\nYou'll get maaaad views."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "I-I'm sorry...! I put myself in so much danger,\r\nand this is how it turns out..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "My influencer days are over...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I even told him to go about it the right way...\r\nWhat an idiot."
msgstr ""

